  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWe should implement the standard `gas_limit` API alongside our implementation of the fee recipient API.\r\n\r\nThe implementation can probably be quite similar to the `feerecipient` API added in #3213.\r\n\r\nWe should also update the docs here, which currently reference the non-standard PATCH API: https://lighthouse-book.sigmaprime.io/builders.html#enabledisable-builder-proposals-and-set-gas-limit\r\n\r\nThe spec is here: https://ethereum.github.io/keymanager-APIs/#/Gas%20Limit\r\n",
